<h2>&#10070; Knowledge Map</h2>
<p>This page distills the <strong>structural knowledge index</strong> (<code>knowledge-index.json</code>) that AI built by reading <strong>every lecture &amp; learning doc under the AI category (the AI galaxy)</strong>. It gathers each doc's <strong>summary, key concepts, and related docs</strong> to show what lives where and <strong>how it all connects</strong>. The <strong>&ldquo;Related Docs&rdquo;</strong> recommendations at the foot of every doc come from the same index. You can also spin these relations in 3D in the <a href="#!cosmos"><strong>&#10022; Knowledge Graph</strong></a>.</p>

<p>All of the wiki's knowledge forms one <strong>Knowledge Universe</strong> &mdash; beneath it sit the <strong>AI galaxy</strong> (lecture &amp; learning knowledge) and the <strong>DOUZONE galaxy</strong> (company &amp; organizational knowledge), each gathering its own clusters. This map covers the <strong>AI galaxy</strong>; work knowledge is aggregated separately in the <a href="#!dz-map"><strong>Douzone Knowledge Map</strong></a>.</p>

